  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Ownership transfer chain: shipping, receiving, and retail sale of a serialized device.",
    "masterDataAvailableFor lists GS1 master data; the gs1: prefix is implicit and omitted inside the block.",
    "Extension properties (electronics:, dpp:) are at EVENT level — including warranty start/end",
    "and purchase country, which used to live in ilmd but EPCIS 2.0 §7.3.8 forbids ilmd on OBSERVE.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: dpp=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,electronics=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/electronics/",
    "See: extensions/common/core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
